# Disable CPU Boost for Legion Go S (SteamOS)

This service disables CPU boost on the Z2 Go chip to reduce operating temperatures and improve battery life. The setting persists across system reboots.

## Installation

Run the following command in the terminal to download and enable the service:

```bash
curl -L [https://raw.githubusercontent.com/](https://raw.githubusercontent.com/)[YOUR_USERNAME]/[YOUR_REPO]/main/install.sh | bash
